info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.present

Class PresentAccepted

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.present.PresentAccepted

  • @Entity
public class PresentAccepted
extends Object
    Presents that are in the in-box of the board a player can accept or deny. If the player accept a present its status is set to accepted and an PresentAccepted object is created.

        public boolean belongsTo(Organisation organisation)
        This method checks if an accepted present belongs to a specific organisation. Therefore it is tested if the organisation's API key matches the present's API key.
        Parameters:
        organisation - The organisation object a present may belongs to.
        Returns:
        Boolean value if the API key of the accepted present is the same of the tested organisation (true) or not (false).
